<div class="title">Awful</div>
<div class="substance">Melatonin & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=NeverAgain&Exact=1">NeverAgain</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; NeverAgain. "Awful: An Experience with Melatonin & Alcohol (exp92093)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 2, 2011. erowid.org/exp/92093</div>

